    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
