    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is immaculate, free from any wear or odors. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a driving experience that is smooth, quiet, and powerful. Every feature and electronic component works exactly as intended, making this a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a like-new vehicle.",
