    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this reliable daily driver! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, this car is still going strong and ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s a budget-friendly option for anyone looking for dependable transportation that gets the job done. Come see for yourself how much life is left in this trusty ride!",
